title: This Is F*cking Weird
description:
Davos where Klaus Schwab has constructed an exclusive zone for the wealthy to virtue signal while pursuing deals. I've been talking to Peter S. Goodman, an award-winning journalist and the author of 'Davos Man: How the Billionaires Devoured the World' about the annual event. #davos #wef #klausschwab

title: Hang On, Could AI Do THIS?!
description:
As Google fires an engineer who claimed the company's artificial intelligence system is conscious, I spoke to Bernardo Kastrup, a computer engineer, philosopher and the author of 'Why Materialism Is Baloney' to ask him about whether A.I really can replace consciousness? Have a look and let me know your thoughts in the comments. #Google #AI #Computer
